To build and install scangearmp:

        ./autogen.sh
        make
        make install

Appendix:

        * You can also set the following path.
           --prefix
                scangearmp                     : default ... /usr/local
           --enable-libpath
                *.tbl,*.DAT,...                : default ... /usr/lib
           --enable-saneconfpath
                *.conf(ex.canon_mfp.conf)      : default ... /usr/lib/bjlib

       Example:

           ./autogen.sh --enable-libpath=/usr/lib
           make
           make install
